withKeyQuotes

TSelf withKeyQuotes(String leftQuote,
                    String rightQuote)
Constructs a new instance with new key prefix and suffix. These values are prepended or appended to each key after its conversion to String during a join.

Parameters:
leftQuote - String to prefix to keys during join. Must not be null, but can be "" (empty string). Example: "(" (left paren/bracket)
rightQuote - String to suffix to keys during join. Must not be null, but can be "" (empty string). Example: ")" (right paren/bracket)
Returns:
new instance with new prefix and suffix for each key
Throws:
NullPointerException - if leftQuote or rightQuote is null
See Also:
